CREATE TABLE `doc-ai-studio.qsight_test.Encounter`
(
  EncounterId STRING NOT NULL,
  CaseNumber INT64,
  AccessionNumber STRING(50),
  ProcedureRoomId STRING NOT NULL,
  DepartmentId STRING NOT NULL,
  EncounterTypeId STRING NOT NULL,
  PatientId STRING,
  PatientVisitId STRING,
  EncounterCostCenterId STRING,
  Comment STRING(1024),
  DateStarted TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateCompleted TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  EncounterStatusId STRING,
  IsArchived BOOL NOT NULL,
  IsDeleted BOOL NOT NULL,
  DeletionReason STRING(255),
  DateCreated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  DateLastModified TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
PARTITION BY DATE(DateCreated);
